captions.text: Hi I'm German, and I bet you a belt that when you fall asleep, you keep breathing.
"Facebook Photos"
I'm starting to look like the singer of an Emo band with this hair.
Pornographies!
I mean photographs!
They say "A picture is worth a thousand words"
And whoever said that, was obviously smoking something quite strong,
because pictures don't speak.
But anyways.
When speaking of photos there's a general rule.
A rule that no one can scape.
No one's the exception.
And the rule is:
No one's as beautiful as their profile picture shows
neither as horrible as their ID picture.
Everyone's embarrassed by their ID picture.
Ok, your sex change treatment is appointed.
Now, I just need your ID to copy your data.
My Identification?
Yes.
Ok but I don't look very good in the picture.
Don't worry, I'm a professional, I'm used to see-
No one escapes the rule.
And that's why you should never trust someone's profile picture.
It's always perfect.
If someone has a profile picture that is TOO perfect.
In real life they probably have 3 nipples,
a wooden leg and an ear on their back.
Hehe, my ex was like that.
Because a profile picture shows the best of someone.
Because they take like a 1000 photos and pick one.
Even a fat ogre with a hairy back looks good if that were the case.
Besides, no one uploads a picture to facebook if they look bad.
Your Facebook profile is perfect.
Only pictures where you look perfect.
Anyone who checks your profile thinks:
"Oh so beautiful!".
Until they see the pictures your friends tag you in.
These photos where you look like shit!.
Because no matter how much you tell your friends not to upload that photo,
they do it anyway!.
And then a green pony came to my house and said to me..
Hi!.
Anyway, please don't upload any of the photos that you took last night because I must look horrible!.
No.
No but really, please don't upload them!.
Really, I promise I won't upload any of the photos I took last night, I promise.
"10 MINUTES LATER"
Uploading, uploading, uploading!.
Son of a bitch!.
And that's when you kiss your dignity goodbye.
A big problem is being alone and wanting to take a picture of yourself.
You have the camera, you have yourself,
but no one to take the picture for you.
So that's when you have to resort to:
Can you take my picture?.
Ask a stranger to take your picture.
Perfect!.
But it can be a little risky.
Thank you for helping me.
No problem, now smile!.
Take a few steps back.
Ok, is here alright?.
A bit further.
Ok, here?.
Just a little bit.
New camera!.
Is here alright?!.
It happens.
It has happened to me many times.
I have a few cameras that I stole, right here
I mean, I mean.
Another common mistake when taking photos is this one:
Ok, take it.
Ok, smile!
Ok, did you take it?.
No, it doesn't work.
But why?, take it already.
I don't know it just doesn't work.
Oh, it was filming.
It always happens!.
And the worst thing is that you always lend the camera to the one who doesn't know how to use it.
You have a film-maker and a technology expert.
But no.
You always give it to the idiot who eats toothpaste.
And because it's your camera, you know how to use it.
So you have to teach the guy, while you're posing.
Ok, take it.
But which button?.
The big one, in the top.
This red one in here?.
No, the one by it, the big one.
Which one?, the green one?.
No, the one that's a bit higher.
I don't know!.
Ok, give me the camera!.
Oh THIS one.
It happens.
Well, technology gets better everyday.
And also with photography.
Photos used to look horrible.
But with the current cameras, photos look spectacular.
Awesome camera.
Thank you my daddy bought it for me.
It's awesome, It's professional right?
Yes.
I don't know if you know but that's one of the best cameras out there.
I imagine the amazing pictures that I could take with a camera like that.
Yeah, you can take great pictures with a camera like this.
Great pictures.
For Facebook!.
I don't understand why people spend 4000 dl on a camera,
to take selfies in the mirror.
It's like those people who go to a restaurant,
and takes pictures of their food to upload on Instagram.
Are you gonna eat?, or audition your french fries to become models?.
And something else I can't understand.
Women of our planet I want to ask you a question.
Who told you you look pretty doing this?.
What's with that duck face?.
It's like you're eating spaghetti.
We are sexy and we eat invisible Spaghetti.
I sincerely don't have the slightest idea-
Fucking hair!
I sincerely don't have the slightest idea,
Of why you think that's sexy.
I've been thinking and I believe
I think we shouldn't see each other anymore.
But why?, don't you love me anymore?.
I love you and you know it but,
but you're horrendous!.
You're so horrendous that every time I see you it makes me want to vom-
And I thought that you called me a horrendous orc, with love.
I thought my hairy back turned you on.
I'm sorry.
It's ok!, I'll leave.
What?.
Make that face again.
What face?,
this one?.
Yes!, you're beautiful, I love you!
You are so beautiful, how didn't I notice it before?.
come here my orc!.
It doesn't happen.
It did happen to a friend.
Shut up!!.
But oh well.
I can't do anything.
Everyone is free to pose however they want to.
But Duck facing is kind of over.
It's not cool anymore.
That's why I bring you some new poses.
So you can use them in your pictures.
"Mauro the dinosaur"
"The kid".
"Chin Chon Chinese"
"Untameable Horse"
"Looking for the Horizon"
"Peeing Dog"
"Looking for the Horizon Pinching my Nose"
"Home Alone"
And the last one but most attractive.
"The Michael Jackson"
But really.
Eventually you have to remember something.
What's on the outside is not what's important.
What matters is what's on the inside.
Like your liver.
What if you don't have a pretty face or perfect body.
If your smile makes the darkest room shine.
Or you better use Photoshop.
QUESTION!
What's your eye color?.
Mine are Brown like poop.
I can see your soul.
It's horrible.
Anyway!.
And this was this week's video, if you liked it please click thumbs up.
Again.
This was this week's video!..
Again.
And this was this week's video, if you liked it please click thumbs up down here.
If you do, I'll give you an x-box, with no contests.
Lying.
If it's the first time you watch one of my videos, subscribe!.
Subscribe!, I upload videos every friday.
A psychological hug and see you next friday!.
And remember, every road takes to Rome.
Except the ones that don't.
Bye Bye!!.
